   <img border="0" height="215" src="/images/dont3.jpg" width="334"/>
   <img border="0" height="215" src="/images/dont4.jpg" width="334"/>
   <br/>
   <br/>
  </p>
  <font face="Arial">
   <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    <br/>
   </p>
  </font>
  This is the general sign for "no."
  <br/>
  You can use either a single or a double motion.  (Meaning, you can close 
  the fingers and thumb either once or twice.)
  <br/>
